wikipedia_page.main: Nathan Boyle (born 14 April 1994) is a football striker who plays for Finn Harps in the League of Ireland.

response: On 15 February 2017, Kennedy was loaned to hometown team Derry City of the League of Ireland until June. He did not score during his time at the Brandywell Stadium, with manager Kenny Shiels preferring to play Nathan Boyle as a lone striker.
